      <title>加拿大央行进一步降息旨在重振低迷的房地产市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/bank-of-canada-s-deeper-cut-aims-to-reignite-a-sluggish-housing-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[房地产市场是加拿大最大的经济引擎之一。加拿大央行目前正试图通过大幅降息来刺激房地产市场，以提振该国疲软的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/bank-of-canada-s-deeper-cut-aims-to-reignite-a-sluggish-housing-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 10:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国央行称德国经济在温和衰退后或将陷入停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/germany-may-be-stagnating-after-mild-recession-bundesbank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行表示，在截至九月的六个月内出现轻微衰退后，德国经济可能在今年年底陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/germany-may-be-stagnating-after-mild-recession-bundesbank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>物价大幅上涨的时代已经结束，美联储感到安心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/era-of-big-price-hikes-is-over-giving-comfort-to-the-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Hobby Works 总裁迈克尔·布雷知道他的客户已经厌倦了涨价，所以他囤积了他认为人们会真正喜欢的低价产品。在马里兰州罗克维尔和劳雷尔的门店，疫情期间火车玩具、遥控汽车和无人机等商品涨价的日子已经一去不复返了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/era-of-big-price-hikes-is-over-giving-comfort-to-the-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库珀称预计欧洲央行不会大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-24/not-expecting-ecb-jumbo-cut-yet-cooper-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nuveen Global 投资策略师 Laura Cooper 讨论了欧洲央行在未来几个月内“大幅降息”的可能性。她在彭博电视台发表讲话时表示，欧元区的服务业通胀率仍然相当高，这表明“降息步伐将逐步加快”。Cooper 补充说，仍然需要“谨慎对待欧洲股市”。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-24/not-expecting-ecb-jumbo-cut-yet-cooper-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 09:52:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国预算担忧迫使企业主关闭公司以避免增税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/uk-budget-fears-push-owners-to-close-firms-to-avoid-tax-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数以千计有偿付能力的英国企业主正在清算他们的公司，以避免预算中对企业家征税的预期增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/uk-budget-fears-push-owners-to-close-firms-to-avoid-tax-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 09:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选前夕欧元对冲价格达到 2017 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/euro-hedges-are-most-overpriced-since-2017-ahead-of-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民意调查显示，美国总统大选前夕对冲欧元的相对成本达到七年来的最高水平，因为投票结果将持续到最后一刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/euro-hedges-are-most-overpriced-since-2017-ahead-of-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 09:29:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴克莱银行第三季度业绩超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-24/barclays-third-quarter-results-beat-expectations-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行第三季度业绩显示，总收入增长 5% 至 65.5 亿英镑（84.9 亿美元），超出分析师预期。这些结果表明，高管们正在兑现他们今年早些时候做出的宏伟承诺，以提高该银行滞后的回报。彭博情报的 Philip Richards 详细分析了这一消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-24/barclays-third-quarter-results-beat-expectations-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 09:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Oaktree 旗下 Banca Progetto 被指控向黑手党提供贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/italy-s-banca-progetto-under-judicial-administration-over-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利 Banca Progetto SpA 因涉嫌向黑手党相关公司提供贷款而被纳入司法管理，在所有者 Oaktree 同意将其出售给 Centerbridge 一个多月后，该银行陷入了危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/italy-s-banca-progetto-under-judicial-administration-over-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 08:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰克冶炼厂受挫加剧供应担忧，伦敦金属交易所锌价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/zinc-hits-20-month-high-on-fears-over-tightening-global-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于主要生产商泰克资源有限公司 (Teck Resources Ltd.) 在其加拿大冶炼厂发生火灾后下调了产量目标，引发了人们对在一系列矿场中断之后的供应的担忧，锌价飙升至 20 个月的盘中高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/zinc-hits-20-month-high-on-fears-over-tightening-global-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 07:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价反弹，关注中东紧张局势和供应前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商继续等待以色列对伊朗采取报复性打击，且美国推动加沙和黎巴嫩停火，油价出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 23:27:45 GMT</pubDate>
